title: Prime Salem Location
posting_body: ['For the most up to date information, visit: <URL>', 'RCG SALEM 978-740-0006', '<URL>', '<URL>', 'Rent Directly From RCG and Pay No Fee!', 'Beautiful luxury unit featuring open kitchen / living area with high ceilings, maple cabinets and granite, wood laminate in the living room and wall to wall carpet in the bedrooms, central AC, washer/dryer in the unit.', 'Elevator in building with on-site parking included in rent.', ' Located in the heart of downtown Salem near many restaurants and shops, the waterfront, and the Peabody Essex Museum.', '  Walking distance to the commuter train station with only a 30-minute commute to Boston.', 'Pet friendly building (One pet limit.', 'Breed and weight restrictions may apply).', ' *Tenant pays Gas (heat), Electric & Water/Sewer.', '*First, last and 1/2 security deposit required *1 year lease term', 'j1f3f9ce8f87c9u']
